Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:28.02,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}星星在呢喃著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.15,0:01:30.94,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}雖然害怕…但還是想！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.44,0:01:36.40,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}光是安穩度日 也太無趣了點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.57,0:01:41.16,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}真希望能改變些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.16,0:01:44.87,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}既然想要個契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:46.54,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}那就飛奔出去吧 Boooon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:50.71,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}回憶在騷動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:56.30,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我…好像認識你！？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.68,0:02:00.43,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不論是晴天雨天還是在下雪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.43,0:02:03.18,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}我都好想好想去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.39,0:02:04.60,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從過去到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:05.85,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}從明天到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.02,0:02:08.73,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}是啊 時間 Nonstop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.94,0:02:14.53,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}先前煩惱的事情 通通都消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.69,0:02:20.41,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}來展開新的故事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:25.50,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}又在做夢嗎？現在的夢還不能說！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.00,0:02:28.33,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}大晴天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.83,0:02:31.00,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}下雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.17,0:02:36.09,OP - ch,,0,0,0,,{\blur5\fad(189,189)}不管是怎樣的天氣 I need you!!
